    SACData

    SACExtension
    Extension of SAC (SAC: seismic analysis code) The basic extensions are Z, R, T (observed).
    SACFile
    SAC file
    (SAC: Seismic analysis code)
    This class is immutable
    SACFileName
    Style of names of SAC files.
    SACHeader
    Information in the header parts of a SAC file.
    SACHeaderData
    Interface of SAC header data
    The SAC header is described here
    SACHeaderEnum
    Header values in a SAC file
    WaveformType
    観測波形(OBS)か理論波形(SYN)か偏微分係数波形(PARTIAL)
